      <pubDate>Fri, 28 Jun 2024 16:54:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>重磅裁决终结了戈萨奇大法官数十年来暗杀雪佛龙的行动</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-28/blockbuster-ruling-caps-gorsuch-s-long-quest-to-gut-agency-power</link>
      <description><![CDATA[大法官尼尔·戈萨奇实现了他数十年的目标，即埋葬了以牺牲法官利益为代价赋予监管机构权力的法律原则。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-28/blockbuster-ruling-caps-gorsuch-s-long-quest-to-gut-agency-power</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 28 Jun 2024 16:47:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国选举活动进行到一半时，工党捐款额超过了保守党</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-28/labour-donations-eclipse-tories-mid-way-through-uk-vote-campaign</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在英国大选活动前半段，个人和组织向反对党工党捐赠了 860 万英镑（1090 万美元），占下周投票前所有向政党捐款的 70% 左右。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-28/labour-donations-eclipse-tories-mid-way-through-uk-vote-campaign</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 28 Jun 2024 16:04:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
